dc_description_s: This ESRI Geodatabase contains polygon features and attribute data tables for census data for the country of Colombia. The data is derived from the Projectado-DANE (Departmento Administrativo Nacional de Estadisticas y Censos) and was released in 2005. The data contain 280,325 census boundary polygons that each have 169 attributes, and the lowest administrative boundary level represented is Manzanas (blocks). Refer to the documentation for a list of variables and a translation of variable titles into English. For more information on the census methodology and a glossary of variable categories, go to the Projecto-DANE website at http://www.dane.gov.co/
